00:15:26,323 --> 00:15:27,825
Bendungan Hoover

182
00:15:27,825 --> 00:15:30,861
Clark County, Nevada

183
00:15:30,861 --> 00:15:32,129
Lawrence, ini luar biasa.

184
00:15:32,129 --> 00:15:34,498
Ini gempa mini ketiga
sejak kita berada di sini.

185
00:15:34,498 --> 00:15:37,168
Denyut magnetiknya telah meningkat
sebelum masing-masingnya.

186
00:15:37,168 --> 00:15:38,936
Kita mendaptkan pola, temanku.

187
00:15:38,936 --> 00:15:40,771
Itu 2,2.

188
00:15:40,771 --> 00:15:42,840
Prediksi model kita.

189
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:44,909
Kita benar menebaknya! Akhirnya!

190
00:15:44,909 --> 00:15:46,911
Ya, benar sekali.

191
00:15:50,347 --> 00:15:51,448
Sial.

192
00:15:53,017 --> 00:15:54,185
Kenapa?

193
00:15:54,185 --> 00:15:56,187
Tingkat denyutnya memuncak lagi.
Mereka sangat besar.

194
00:15:56,921 --> 00:15:58,022
Apa kau serius?

195
