Kim?

196
00:16:01,425 --> 00:16:03,127
Kita akan mengalami gempa besar.

197
00:16:09,366 --> 00:16:10,868
Itu melompat ke 7,1!

198
00:16:11,769 --> 00:16:12,837
Astaga, Kim!

199
